# .env
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your Firebase values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to git — it's already in .gitignore.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser bundle.
# These values are NOT secret (Firebase web config is public-facing by design),
# but keeping them in .env prevents them from being hardcoded and visible in
# plain text in your source files.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

